{"tid":225017,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2017 DSE] 英文oral討論","createTime":"2017-05-01T13:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T07:52:03.000Z","uid":12873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b948bda1a5008c9d978b27fffba9d6d30b3f6427","tid":225017,"uid":12873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"聽日就係oral既開始 對於大部分人 呢科都應該最後一科了(除咗仲未考旅款同文學既人） <br />\n大家考完就擺d題目同IR問題上黎傾下 造福下未考既人啦<br />\n最後一科 要考好d呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞過5**/有心得既人就分享下自己既經驗啦 相信好多人都好需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b349401a0543299df2234db45d6225b900b675","tid":225017,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"Oral有冇咩要準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c15c0d09b85e16c1d7bad8b12c301e69f5c286","tid":225017,"uid":9187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"唔温啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9cc75c383e0bf2825416ca7842359a265a4cb9","tid":225017,"uid":425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"想問下oral如果係一個分題到有人持相反意見應唔應該駁<br />\n定每個分題輪流講下就ok 唔洗駁羸人"},{"pid":"5f002d12f6a129620a039bef58e893a16ba0b4f0","tid":225017,"uid":27741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n可能有啲阿媽係女人，不過諗到啲咩照講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1: 如果你冇超時講野而有人亂打斷你，<br />\n唔好淆底，有禮貌提出你仲有野要講，<br />\n唔好show個唔耐煩同嬲嘅樣。<br />\n可以<span style=\"color: red;\">微笑加用輕鬆語氣</span>講<br />\nOh (停半秒) (could you) Please allow me to finish(?)<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">(你喜歡可以舉起食指/成隻手到大概膊頭位 手指尖少少斜向前 一來會draw attention 二來可以表達出你冷靜，唔係私私縮縮。當然唔好指住人<br />\n都適用於你有個好重要嘅point要講時吸引考官留意)</span><br />\n平時傾計我會建議講完依句停兩秒先 再加返啲有謙虛嘅引入。不過考試interrupt人嘅撚樣通常都冇乜禮貌同好心急，未必會讓你。<br />\n道理喺你度，考官都會明。你講完依句直接繼續你自己野就ok。<br />\n即係例如 oh (could you) please allow me to finish(?) (Pause半秒) what I was talking about is blah blah blah 咁樣入返。<br />\n<br />\n2: 講錯野發錯音嗰啲，自我即刻糾正可以表示到你係識，只係口快講錯。<br />\n唔好因為噏錯一個字之後騰晒雞。<br />\n輕微嘅grammatical mistakes扮冇事直接skip<br />\n<br />\n3: 如果有point好想加都要睇值唔值得。<br />\n你無啦啦加啲冇乜內容嘅野，可能印象會差啲。而且又唔好彩令一個未發言而又想發言嘅人miss左發言機會會顯得你小家，次數多甚至被認為壟斷發言。<br />\n<br />\n4: 唔好淨係focus喺背自己啲point度，要留意他人說話。<br />\n每次發言都要承接之前啲人講嘅野，<br />\n最好一句過回應其他人再加自己個point。同埋要改用另一啲用字講佢個論點。<br />\n例如題目係why does small Ming win?<br />\ncandidate A話 small Ming wins because he runs faster than a train<br />\n你承接就講it's true that small Ming is a quick runner with enthusiasm<br />\n咁你就認同左A講佢跑得快，同時加左佢有enthusiasm。可以俾到人錯覺你有正式回應對家又可以輕輕提出你個論點。<br />\n接下來就一句topic sentence。 being passionate about running is also very important. Small Ming sets goals and blah blah blah...<br />\n但回應時儘量唔好指明邊個candidate，唔好抛個波益左佢俾佢回應你。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c80b44976d2c4fdb7b301a6808c689023437e63f","tid":225017,"uid":66448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"其實英文oral 唔搶野講會唔人1次都講唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c079c003f619c8207825e96196085913d9ed7f45","tid":225017,"uid":66448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實英文oral 唔搶野講會唔人1次都講唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會</span>"},{"pid":"c6629424212c0dd077fd33dd2bfb1f2121e1c3ac","tid":225017,"uid":12873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實英文oral 唔搶野講會唔人1次都講唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會</span></blockquote><br />\n要睇下你d組員係咪aggressive 正常應該會invite你講野既"},{"pid":"8f423c9ebff8ca9da6e959fda1dcba75c775f3f8","tid":225017,"uid":16226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"唉聽日考 好驚"},{"pid":"1c2aa97088896e98fdd9a10798b1aaa7dc6b40b8","tid":225017,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:15:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位點都要入去睇一睇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">各位DSE雞唔該入一入黎</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/2?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"9b22aa13b273639b017e6af15653ceb00f3840a6","tid":225017,"uid":12873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"各位比心機呀 考完就share下題目啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}